          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/51475154-monogamy-book-one-lover">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3197519376" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2450129559572830182">I’m just grateful for the firework of emotions, when you read chokingly, through the night, and with tears in your eyes. I’m grateful for the pages that you re-read and re-read, for such vivid and real !!! and meaningful!!! characters. For my beloved Lera and Alex! <br/>And a special thank you for the soundtracks!!! They are such an icing on the cake that makes the whole story encompassing, colorful and vibrant! Thanks!!! <br/>And for those who are still pondering – by all means read this book! <br/> <br/>The ARC i</span>
  <span id="freeText2450129559572830182" style="display:none">I’m just grateful for the firework of emotions, when you read chokingly, through the night, and with tears in your eyes. I’m grateful for the pages that you re-read and re-read, for such vivid and real !!! and meaningful!!! characters. For my beloved Lera and Alex! <br />And a special thank you for the soundtracks!!! They are such an icing on the cake that makes the whole story encompassing, colorful and vibrant! Thanks!!! <br />And for those who are still pondering – by all means read this book! <br /> <br />The ARC is provided by the author for an honest review.</span>
