  <span id="freeText10868299225265688016" style="display:none">4.5<br /><br />❤😆❤🔥🔥😢😭 <br /><br />I love her style of writing Victoria adds music's title to each chapter or a moment between the characters <br /><br />I need part 2 !!!!<br /><br />I haven't read a bot like this before. So Valeria/Lena has a son Danny and a lazy ass of a husband. Then cam Alex who is a friend. Then friendship turned into love. She has affair with Alex and it that love that you couldn't live without. She ends it and she does regret, when she didn't find him at his home.<br /><br />5 years later...😢 Alex is sick and his sister Maria well actually we learn is his cousin. But she is more of a sister. Calls her and ask her to save him cause he is refusing treatment to help him. It's hard to watch someone you love getting weaker and weaker every passing day. They started to get close again and Alex is getting stronger <br />THEN...his bitch of a wife Hannah (his heart only belong to Lena) tell her she is no longer needed and she said go home. And she refuse until she feels Alex from the stairs. He said go home too. <br /><br />2 and half months she stayed with the love of her life. Help him heal and get him to live again. Then its ends !! <br /><br />I care more about Alex than the heroine. I hope in the second book that my feeling towards her change.<br /><br />Has he fully recover??? <br />Will Alex and Lena finally leave their husband &amp; wife to be together ??? <br />Too many questions !!!!!!</span>
