  <span id="freeText9215199060967375369" style="display:none"> <p>After I read this book, I had a runner's high! It was this feeling of euphoria as if a new lease of life for me began. I am very happy now, and I always was very happy. I have everything that any average woman dreams of (I won’t list, so as not to jinx it - I’m superstitious to hell), but <strong>after reading this book, it’s as if something clicked and turned into rainbow colors</strong>. Someone makes their life brighter with the help of alcohol, drugs, sex, and for me it is reading books, good books. I’ll write a worthy review after my second reading,  when I cool down and gather my thoughts.​<em></em> </p></span>
