  <span id="freeText17964226224894275320" style="display:none">So i have read the two of the books back to back. I wont lie. This is absolutely beautiful. What i want to say it is real. Thisis real people and understanding. It was really beautiful and everything is really refreshing, lovely and this was so heart fulfilling. Every emotion being touched so beautifully. I can't complain. This writer has me begging for the third book to the point i want to know whats going in her brain. Marvellous read and before anyone has got to say anything bad about it, I would like to tell you to stop. This book is for people who have matured a bit. Who aren't living in dreams. This is different. This is real. It is refined and beautiful.<br />Please let me know when is the third book coming out. I just want to know how these two people go because there were promises and how do they end. Either way i love it.<br /><br />Forgive me for mistakes if I wrote while walking.</span>
