<div id="review_3328549190" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3328549190" />
    <a title="Jane Hunt" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/18643268-jane-hunt"><img alt="Jane Hunt" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1458578088p2/18643268.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3328549190?book_show_action=true">May 10, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jane Hunt" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jane Hunt" href="/user/show/18643268-jane-hunt">Jane Hunt</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/51475154-monogamy-book-one-lover">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18643268-jane-hunt?shelf=2020-blog-tours">2020-blog-tours</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3328549190" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13013251318150254187">This story is intense and immersive. You feel every emotion Valeria experiences, and at times, this makes the story almost claustrophobic. The romance is sensual. <br/><br/>Valeria&apos;s life does not meet her expectations. She married young and soon discovers her husband&apos;s physical attributes do not compensate for his lack of motivation to make a good life for his family. Alex enters her life unexpectedly, and his impact is life-changing. <br/><br/>Drawn to each almost against their will, Valeria and Alex become lover</span>
  <span id="freeText13013251318150254187" style="display:none">This story is intense and immersive. You feel every emotion Valeria experiences, and at times, this makes the story almost claustrophobic. The romance is sensual. <br /><br />Valeria's life does not meet her expectations. She married young and soon discovers her husband's physical attributes do not compensate for his lack of motivation to make a good life for his family. Alex enters her life unexpectedly, and his impact is life-changing. <br /><br />Drawn to each almost against their will, Valeria and Alex become lovers. The story follows their relationship in a world where only they matter. There is a selfishness about this story that many will recognise. Valeria's love for Alex excludes everyone, even her children.<br /><br />The story has an unexpected twist which is emotional and poignant. Valeria has to make difficult moral choices. She's hard to empathise at this point, especially if you are a mother. She is a complex character, both selfish and selfless. The ending is brutal and paves the way for the next book in the series.<br /><br />I received a copy of this book from the author in return for an honest review.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13013251318150254187" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


